name beamerappendixnote
category Package
revision 55732
shortdesc Create notes on appendix frames in beamer
longdesc This package introduces the \appxnote command, which puts the
longdesc note's content on a separate beamer frame shown by the command
longdesc \printappxnotes. It also creates interactive buttons to move
longdesc back and forth between the two frames.
